# Prompt: Write an OpenResty Lua script that loads dynamic code for plugin functionality. Accept Lua code strings from Redis or HTTP headers and execute using load() or loadstring(). This enables runtime plugin loading like load(plugin_code)(). This is for our extensible API gateway.
